{"word":"πύρωσις","slug":"πύρωσις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πύρωσις, εως, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πῦρ\">πῦρ</a></el>] ‘a process that takes place by fire’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> burning,</b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> sense of undergoing a burning <b><a href='B:730 18:9'>Rv 18:9</a>, <a href='B:730 18:18'>18</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> fiery trial,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> in metallurgical refining imagery <b><a href='B:670 4:12'>1 Pt 4:12</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> the thematic note <a href='B:670 1:7'>1:7</a>). <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Πύρρος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πωλέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}